DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages glassfish
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include glassfish              # Install and run glassfish with standard configurations.
include glassfish::disable     # Disable glassfish service.
include glassfish::disableboot # Disable glassfish service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include glassfish::absent      # Remove glassfish package.

DEPENDENCIES:
